Subject: [PATCH] hwui: Disable fine-grained logging

We're using the default OpenGL renderer, which I don't think anyone plans on debugging

diff --git a/libs/hwui/Android.bp b/libs/hwui/Android.bp
index f167f3e2fdf..b996c78e8f2 100644
--- a/libs/hwui/Android.bp
+++ b/libs/hwui/Android.bp
@@ -248,7 +248,7 @@ cc_library {
         // Enables fine-grained GLES error checking
         // If enabled, every GLES call is wrapped & error checked
         // Has moderate overhead
-        "hwui_enable_opengl_validation",
+        //"hwui_enable_opengl_validation",
 ],
 }
 
